Package: termr
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, vlc, python3-textual, python3-requests, python3-rich
Description: Terminal-based radio player with TUI
 Termr is a terminal-based radio player with a text user interface (TUI).
 It allows you to browse, favorite and play radio stations from the Radio Browser API.
 .
 Features:
  * Browse radio stations from Radio Browser API
  * Play, pause, favorite and stop radio streams
  * Manage favorite stations
  * Simple TUI interface
  * Low memory usage
  * Cross-platform support
